*desklet-temperature-0.1 (09 Oct 2003)

  09 Oct 2003; Mike Gardiner <obz@gentoo.org> desklet-temperature-0.1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  First version of the temperature desklet which provides an evolutionary view
  of temperature changes, rather than just a single atomic reading

